snippet.title: Render96 2.0 Release Trailer!
snippet.description:
Check us out: https://linktr.ee/Render96

Video made by ATi Plays
Check him out over at his channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjzTw4FXHiVda1x_Gf56w1w?view_as=subscriber

Thanks to Qumu for their remixes!
Check them out over at their channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0QbcOX2gI5zruEvpSmnf6Q

**Render96 : Base Models V2.0**
+ All models have been either optimized/remodeled. 
+ Updated textures for models

+ Added a new bowser with custom animations/rig
+ Added Motos with new custom animations/rig (Spawns removed because of crashing sorry!)
+ Added Ice bullies
+ Added a HD Goddard
+ Added a new title screen
+ Added new bowser bomb models

+ Updated Mario and Luigi's models
+ Fixed Luigi X eye texture bug
+ Luigi now has slippery controls
+ Removed flutter jump from Luigi's second jump
+ Dynamic Hud with multiple life icons

+ Fixed scuttlebug's eye texture

Bowser will be released but it is not final.
